OL,3,CAssisted dying: Will potential law in
OL,4,CJersey catalyse nationwide change?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Multimedia Producer
OL,7,FAlicia Curry
OL,9,FIn a landmark move, the island of has
OL,10,Fpublished proposals for an assisted
OL,11,Fdying law.
OL,13,FA debate is scheduled for May but the
OL,14,Finitial draft published on Friday by
OL,15,Fthe States Assembly - the island's
OL,16,Flegislative body - would allow
OL,17,Fterminally ill adults who have lived
OL,18,Fon Jersey for 12 months to have the
OL,19,Foption to end their lives with medical
OL,20,Fassistance.
