OL,3,CAssisted dying: Will potential law in
OL,4,CJersey catalyse nationwide change?
OL,6,FWhile advocates hail it as a step
OL,7,Ftowards compassionate end of life
OL,8,Fcare, critics raise concerns about how
OL,9,Fethical the decision is.
OL,11,FIt has also reignited the conversation
OL,12,Fover being accessible to the rest of
OL,13,Fthe UK. While the issue has been
OL,14,Fbrought to Parliament several times,
OL,15,Fthere has never been nationwide
OL,16,Fenactment.
OL,18,FHere, ITV News explains whether
OL,19,FJersey's move will serve as a catalyst
OL,20,Ffor change elsewhere in the UK.
