OL,6,FWhy is there so much debate around it?
OL,8,Fthat an overwhelming majority of the
OL,9,Fpublic are in favour of assisted
OL,10,Fdying, according to the largest poll
OL,11,Fever conducted.
OL,13,FAround 75% of people said they support
OL,14,Fa change in the law, versus 14% who
OL,15,Fare opposed.
OL,17,F"It offers peace of mind that there
OL,18,Fare options there, nobody has to use
OL,19,Fit but it does derive a comfort," Fran
OL,20,FHall, Dignity in Dying's Campaigns and
OL,21,FEngagement Manager, told ITV News.
