OL,6,FTanya Tupper's mum had planned to
OL,7,Ftravel abroad to end her life because
OL,8,Fshe was in so much pain, but she ended
OL,9,Fup becoming too ill to make the journey
OL,11,FBut adversaries say it could lead to
OL,12,Fpeople dying "prematurely" under the
OL,13,Fpressure of being a "burden on their
OL,14,Ffamily" and pose moral questions for
OL,15,Fmedical professionals.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for charity Care Not
OL,18,FKilling told ITV News that legalising
OL,19,Fassisted dying "would put a huge
OL,20,Famount of pressure on elderly and
OL,21,Fvulnerable people to die prematurely".
