OL,6,FSpeaking in a phone call filmed by ITV
OL,7,FNews, Sir Keir said he was "personally
OL,8,Fcommitted" to a change in the law.
OL,10,FMSPs are currently considering a
OL,11,Fprivate members' bill in the Scottish
OL,12,Fparliament, while the Isle of Man
OL,13,Fvoted last year to legalise assisted
OL,14,Fdying, meaning it will likely become
OL,15,Fthe first country in the British isles
OL,16,Fto introduce it.
OL,18,FThe government does not typically take
OL,19,Fa position on assisted dying and
OL,20,Finstead considers it a matter for MPs
