OL,6,FHow would it come into law nationwide?
OL,8,FA draft proposal of legislation
OL,9,Fregarding assisted dying would need to
OL,10,Fbe constructed by an MP or a member of
OL,11,Fthe House of Lords.
OL,13,FIt would then be formally introduced
OL,14,Fin chamber through a first reading.
OL,15,FAfter this, the bill would typically
OL,16,Fproceed to a committee for detailed
OL,17,Fscrutiny.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/15
